{"type":"message","id":"0dc8c484","parentId":"005152b8","timestamp":"2026-06-11T13:39:39.170Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"备份完成。现在开始精确修复：\n\n## 修复 1: 对焦+/- 功能\n\n检查 `continuous_move` 方法中 focus 参数的传递："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6846d8ce3d1f487cbc5cd500","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":1062,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/core/ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":76447,"output":77,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76524,"cost":{"input":0.076447,"output":0.0002464,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0766934}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781185164504,"responseId":"cht000e6033@dx19eb6e8d58ab893102"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e0cf76c9","parentId":"0dc8c484","timestamp":"2026-06-11T13:39:39.218Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6846d8ce3d1f487cbc5cd500","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def continuous_move(self, pan: float = 0, tilt: float = 0, zoom: float = 0, focus: float = 0) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"连续移动 PTZ。\r\n\r\n        ISAPI 2.0 格式: panSpeed/tiltSpeed 范围 -10(left/down) 到 10(right/up),\r\n        zoomSpeed -10(out) 到 10(in), focusSpeed -10(near) 到 10(far), 0 = stop.\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        # 将 0-100 范围映射到 -10..10 (ISAPI 2.0 规范)\r\n        pan_speed = round(pan / 10.0)\r\n        tilt_speed = round(tilt / 10.0)\r\n        zoom_speed = round(zoom / 10.0)\r\n        focus_speed = round(focus / 10.0)\r\n\r\n        # 停止移动：使用 /continuous 端点速度全0\r\n        if pan_speed == 0 and tilt_speed == 0 and zoom_speed == 0 and focus_speed == 0:\r\n            xml = '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>'\r\n            xml += '<PTZData version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">'\r\n            xml += '<ptzSpeed>'\r\n            xml += '<pan>0</pan><tilt>0</tilt><zoom>0</zoom><focus>0</focus>'\r\n            xml += '</ptzSpeed></PTZData>'\r\n            result = self.client.put(f\"{self._ptz_base()}/continuous\", xml)\r\n            return result.status_code == 200\r\n\r\n        xml = f\"\"\"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<PTZData version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n  <ptzSpeed>\r\n    <pan>{pan_speed}</pan>\r\n    <tilt>{tilt_speed}</tilt>\r\n    <zoom>{zoom_speed}</zoom>\r\n    <focus>{focus_speed}</focus>\r\n  </ptzSpeed>\r\n</PTZData>\"\"\"\r\n        result = self.client.put(f\"{self._ptz_base()}/continuous\", xml)\r\n        return result.status_code == 200\r\n\r\n    def stop_move(self) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"停止连续移动。\"\"\"\r\n        return self.continuous_move(0, 0, 0, 0)\r\n\r\n    def continuous_move_duration(self, pan: float, tilt: flo