{"type":"message","id":"87e3bbd0","parentId":"9f7fdbf0","timestamp":"2026-06-11T13:48:13.203Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f0ec4578ae6145af894dd883","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        // 对焦控制\r\n        function ptzFocus(mode) {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\r\n            var dir = mode === 'auto' ? 'focus-auto' : mode === 'near' ? 'focus-near' : 'focus-far';\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/move', {\r\n                direction: dir,\r\n                speed: parseInt(document.getElementById('ptzSpeed').value)\r\n            }).catch(function(e) { addLog('info', 'PTZ 对焦: ' + mode); });\r\n        }\r\n        function setFocusMode(mode) {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/focus/mode', { mode: mode }).then(function(result) {\r\n                if (result && result.success) {\r\n                    showToast('success', '对焦模式: ' + mode);\r\n                } else {\r\n                    showToast('error', result ? result.message : '设置失败');\r\n                }\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n\n[506 more lines in file. Use offset=2005 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781185693203}}
{"type":"message","id":"4745be77","parentId":"87e3bbd0","timestamp":"2026-06-11T13:49:00.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在进行精确修复。根据代码分析：\n\n## 问题根源\n\n1. **焦距+/- 不工作**：当设备处于半自动（SEMIAUTOMATIC）或自动（AUTO）模式时，手动 focus+/- 不会生效。需要在手动模式（MANUAL）下才能使用。\n\n2. **OSD 速度慢**：代码逻辑正确，ISAPI 响应时间约 46ms。如果感觉慢，可能是网络延迟或前端渲染问题。\n\n让我修改前端代码，使 focus+/- 按钮在按下时自动切换到手动模式："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-dbbab64991d546ce95794f26f965a3fe","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        // 对焦调整：focus+/- 需要手动模式，自动切换\n        function ptzFocus(mode) {\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\n            \n            // focus+/- 需要手动对焦模式，先切换\n            if (mode === 'near' || mode === 'far') {\n                // 先设置为手动模式\n                apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/focus/mode', { mode: 'manual' }).then(function(result) {\n                    if (result && result.success) {\n                        // 更新下拉框显示\n                        var sel = document.getElementById('focusMode');\n                        if (sel) sel.value = 'manual';\n                        showToast('info', '已切换到手动对焦模式');\n                        \n                        // 然后发送 focus 移动指令\n                        var dir = mode === 'near' ? 'focus-near' : 'focus-far';\n                        apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/move', {\n                            direction: dir,\n                            speed: parseInt(document.getElementById('ptzSpeed').value)\n                        }).catch(function(e) { addLog('info', 'PTZ 对焦: ' + mode); });\n                    } else {\n                        showToast('error', '切换手动对焦失败');\n                    }\n                }).catch(function(e) { \n                    showToast('error', '切换手动对焦异常: ' + e.message); \n                });\n            } else if (mode === 'auto') {\n                // 自动对焦直接调用\n                apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/move', {\n                    direction: 'focus-auto',\n                    speed: 0\n                }).catch(function(e) { addLog('info', 'PTZ 对焦: auto'); });\n            }\n        }","oldText":"        // 对焦调整\n        function ptzFocus(mode) {\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\n            var dir = mode === 'auto' ? 'focus-auto' : mode === 'near' ? 'focus-near' : 'focus-far';\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/move', {\n                direction: dir,\n                speed: parseInt(document.getElementById('ptzSpeed').value)\n            }).catch(function(e) { addLog('info', 'PTZ 对焦: ' + mode); });\n        }"}],"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":84910,"output":757,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85667,"cost":{"input":0.08491,"output":0.0024224000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0873324}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781185693206,"responseId":"cht000dcac2@dx19eb6f0eccdb8ab282"}}
