{"type":"message","id":"6b8546ed","parentId":"eddfee00","timestamp":"2026-06-11T17:21:42.679Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**找到根因了！**\n\n| 操作 | PTZ OSD | OSD Info |\n|------|---------|----------|\n| GET | 69.7ms | 31.7ms |\n| Parse | 0.1ms | 0.1ms |\n| PUT | 51.7ms | **2169.9ms** |\n\n**OSD Info 的 PUT 操作本身就很慢（2.17秒）！** 这是海康设备的特性，不是代码问题。\n\n让我验证是否是因为发送的 XML 不完整导致设备处理慢："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6998ca3faf244585a207cc35","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X GET \"http://192.168.5.72/ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/overlays\" --digest -u admin:Nftw1357 --max-time 10 2>&1 > C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\overlays_orig.xml && echo \"Saved original XML\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":114257,"output":203,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114460,"cost":{"input":0.114257,"output":0.0006496000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1149066}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781198490853,"responseId":"cht000d7ca2@dx19eb7b413b1b828232"}}
