{"type":"message","id":"48c250bb","parentId":"7e898418","timestamp":"2026-06-11T17:23:16.370Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"生成的 XML 是完整的（898 chars vs 原始 931 chars，差异只是格式化）。\n\n**结论：OSD Info 的 PUT 操作慢是海康设备的特性，不是代码问题。** 设备处理 VideoOverlay 的 PUT 需要约 2 秒。\n\n但老板要求两者速度基本相等。我需要换个思路：**不发送完整 XML，只发送需要修改的部分**。让我检查海康是否支持部分更新："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c0ab3f017a324e4580eec31e","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"Test partial XML PUT - only DateTimeOverlay\"\"\"\nimport time\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\n\nIP = \"192.168.5.72\"\nAUTH = HTTPDigestAuth(\"admin\", \"Nftw1357\")\n\n# Test 1: Only DateTimeOverlay endpoint\nprint(\"=== Test DateTimeOverlay only ===\")\nendpoint_dt = f\"http://{IP}/ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/overlays/DateTimeOverlay\"\nxml_dt = '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?><DateTimeOverlay><enabled>true</enabled></DateTimeOverlay>'\n\nstart = time.time()\nresp = requests.put(endpoint_dt, auth=AUTH, data=xml_dt, headers={\"Content-Type\": \"application/xml\"}, timeout=10)\nelapsed = (time.time() - start) * 1000\nprint(f\"PUT DateTimeOverlay: {elapsed:.1f}ms, HTTP {resp.status_code}\")\n\n# Test 2: Only channelNameOverlay endpoint\nprint(\"\\n=== Test channelNameOverlay only ===\")\nendpoint_cn = f\"http://{IP}/ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/overlays/channelNameOverlay\"\nxml_cn = '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?><channelNameOverlay><enabled>true</enabled></channelNameOverlay>'\n\nstart = time.time()\nresp = requests.put(endpoint_cn, auth=AUTH, data=xml_cn, headers={\"Content-Type\": \"application/xml\"}, timeout=10)\nelapsed = (time.time() - start) * 1000\nprint(f\"PUT channelNameOverlay: {elapsed:.1f}ms, HTTP {resp.status_code}\")","path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/test_partial_put.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":116401,"output":475,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTok