{"type":"message","id":"4d01d98a","parentId":"b97d7503","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:00:17.771Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"发现问题了！\n\n**问题1：zoom 按钮问题**\n- `ptzZoom` 函数发送 API 后没有 `.then()` 处理，只有 `.catch()` 错误处理\n- 这意味着即使 API 返回成功，前端也不会有任何反馈\n\n**问题2：对焦问题**\n- 我之前修改的代码强制切换到手动模式，但老板说半自动模式也可以手动移动焦点\n- 需要移除强制切换逻辑\n\n**问题3：OSD 问题**\n- 需要检查官方 ISAPI 的正确用法\n\n让我读取完整的 ptzZoom 和 ptzFocus 函数："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-e37e0b55bd244eb3903efc7b49aa24c4","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":1976,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":132919,"output":174,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133093,"cost":{"input":0.13291899999999998,"output":0.0005568000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.13347579999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781200794103,"responseId":"cht000dad6e@dx19eb7d74c26ba5b442"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d3fad8d6","parentId":"4d01d98a","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:00:17.781Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-e37e0b55bd244eb3903efc7b49aa24c4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function ptzZoom(direction) {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\r\n            var speed = parseInt(document.getElementById('ptzSpeed').value);\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/move', {\r\n                direction: direction === 'in' ? 'zoom-in' : 'zoom-out',\r\n                speed: speed\r\n            }).catch(function(e) { addLog('info', 'PTZ 变焦: ' + direction); });\r\n        }\r\n        // 对焦控制\r\n        // 对焦调整：focus+/- 需要手动模式，自动切换\r\n        function ptzFocus(mode) {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\r\n            \r\n            // focus+/- 需要手动对焦模式，先切换\r\n            if (mode === 'near' || mode === 'far') {\r\n                // 先设置为手动模式\r\n                apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/focus/mode', { mode: 'manual' }).then(function(result) {\r\n                    if (result && result.success) {\r\n                        // 更新下拉框显示\r\n                        var sel = document.getElementById('focusMode');\r\n                        if (sel) sel.value = 'manual';\r\n                        showToast('info', '已切换到手动对焦模式');\r\n                        \r\n                        // 然后发送 focus 移动指令\r\n                        var dir = mode === 'near' ? 'focus-near' : 'focus-far';\r\n                        apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/move', {\r\n                            direction: dir,\r\n                            speed: parseInt(document.getElementById('ptzSpeed').value)\r\n                        }).catch(function(e) { addLog('info', 'PTZ 对焦: ' + mode); });\r\n                    } else {\r\n                        showToast('error', '切换手动对焦失败');\r\n                    }\r\n                }).catch(function(e) { \r\n                    showToast('error', '切换手动对焦异常: ' + e.message); \r\n                });\r\n            } else if (mode === 'auto') {\r\n                // 自动对焦直接调用\r\n                apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/move', {\r\n                    direction: 'focus-auto',\r\n                    speed: 0\r\n                }).catch(function(e) { addLog('info', 'PTZ 对焦: auto'); });\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        function setFocusMode(mode) {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/focus/mode', { mode: mode }).then(function(result) {\r\n                if (result && result.success) {\r\n\n[511 more lines in file. Use offset=2026 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781200817781}}
{"type":"message","id":"533c7e66","parentId":"d3fad8d6","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:00:39.410Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在修复：\n\n## 修复计划\n\n**问题1：zoom 按钮无反馈**\n- 原因：`ptzZoom` 函数只有 `.catch()` 没有 `.then()`\n- 修复：添加 `.then()` 处理\n\n**问题2：对焦问题**\n- 老板说半自动模式下可以手动移动焦点，不需要强制切换\n- 修复：移除强制切换到手动模式的逻辑，直接发送 focus 移动指令\n\n**问题3：OSD 问题**\n- 需要检查官方 ISAPI 使用方式\n- 可能需要使用不同的端点或方法\n\n修复前端代码："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-8cf42097387e41688b024c5a8d151e02","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        function ptzZoom(direction) {\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\n            var speed = parseInt(document.getElementById('ptzSpeed').value);\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/move', {\n                direction: direction === 'in' ? 'zoom-in' : 'zoom-out',\n                speed: speed\n            }).then(function(result) {\n                if (result && result.success) {\n                    addLog('info', '变焦: ' + direction + ' (速度=' + speed + ')');\n                } else {\n                    showToast('error', result ? result.message : '变焦失败');\n                }\n            }).catch(function(e) { showToast('error', '变焦异常: ' + e.message); });\n        }","oldText":"        function ptzZoom(direction) {\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\n            var speed = parseInt(document.getElementById('ptzSpeed').value);\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/move', {\n                direction: direction === 'in' ? 'zoom-in' : 'zoom-out',\n                speed: speed\n            }).catch(function(e) { addLog('info', 'PTZ 变焦: ' + direction); });\n        }"}],"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":133723,"output":513,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134236,"cost":{"input":0.13372299999999998,"output":0.0016416000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.13536459999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781200817786,"responseId":"cht000d9cf3@dx19eb7d7ad65ba5a412"}}
