{"type":"message","id":"3793e7ce","parentId":"e5d79ac8","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:13:44.283Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## v5.47 修复汇报\n\n**修复内容**：\n1. **Zoom 按钮**：添加 `.then()` 处理成功响应\n2. **Focus 按钮**：移除强制切换手动模式的逻辑，直接发送 focus 移动指令\n\n**OSD Info 延迟说明**：\n- 海康设备处理 VideoOverlay PUT 需要 **约 2 秒**（设备固有特性）\n- PTZ OSD 只需要 **约 80ms**（XML 更小，处理更快）\n- 两者速度差异是设备端点不同导致的，**无法通过代码优化解决**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":152444,"output":126,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":152570,"cost":{"input":0.152444,"output":0.00040320000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1528472}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781201614030,"responseId":"cht000d241a@dx19eb7e3be99b9ca102"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5f1aeeb8","parentId":"3793e7ce","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:14:51.425Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"32811\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-06-12 02:14 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n你现在，完全模拟用户鼠标点击操作，playwrite，操作astrohub，检查zoom、focus是否都实现了"}],"timestamp":1781201691419}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a0c477f","parentId":"5f1aeeb8","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:15:41.623Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到。使用 Playwright 完整模拟用户操作，验证 Zoom 和 Focus 功能。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-109c164aaa544bfd9f6ac6551192adb0","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nv5.47 E2E Test - Complete User Flow Simulation\nSimulate real user mouse clicks on AstroHub web UI\n\"\"\"\nimport time\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright, expect\n\nBASE_URL = \"http://localhost:10280\"\nDEVICE_IP = \"192.168.5.72\"\n\ndef test_zoom_focus_e2e():\n    with sync_playwright() as p:\n        browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True)\n        context = browser.new_context()\n        page = context.new_page()\n        \n        print(\"=\" * 60)\n        print(\"AstroHub E2E Test - Zoom & Focus\")\n        print(\"=\" * 60)\n        \n        # 1. Open main page\n        print(\"\\n1. Opening AstroHub main page...\")\n        page.goto(BASE_URL, timeout=30000)\n        page.wait_for_load_state('networkidle')\n        print(\"   Page loaded\")\n        \n        # 2. Navigate to Console page\n        print(\"\\n2. Navigating to Console page...\")\n        try:\n            # Find and click Console nav button\n            console_btn = page.locator('[data-page=\"console\"]')\n            if console_btn.count() > 0:\n                console_btn.click()\n                page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n                print(\"   Console page opened\")\n            else:\n                print(\"   ERROR: Console button not found\")\n                return False\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"   ERROR: {e}\")\n            return False\n        \n        # 3. Check if device is connected\n        print(\"\\n3. Checking device connection status...\")\n        try:\n            status_text = page.locator('#deviceStatus')\n            if status_text.count() > 0:\n                status = status_text.text_content()\n                print(f\"   Status: {status}\")\n                \n                # If not connected, connect device\n                if \"未连接\" in status or status == \"\":\n                    print(\"   Device not connected, connecting...\")\n                    # Click device selector\n                    device_select = page.locator('#ptzDeviceSelect')\n                    if device_select.count() > 0:\n                        device_select.select_option(DEVICE_IP)\n                        page.wait_for_timeout(500)\n                        \n                        # Click connect button\n                        connect_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"连接\")')\n                        if connect_btn.count() > 0:\n                            connect_btn.click()\n                            page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n                            print(\"   Connected\")\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"   Warning: {e}\")\n        \n        # 4. Get initial position\n        print(\"\\n4. Getting initial PTZ position...\")\n        try:\n            position_div = page.locator('#ptzPosition')\n            if position_div.count() > 0:\n                initial_pos = position_div.text_content()\n                print(f\"   Initial: {initial_pos}\")\n                # Parse zoom value\n                import re\n                zoom_match = re.search(r'Zoom:\\s*(\\d+)', initial_pos)\n                initial_zoom = int(zoom_match.group(1)) if zoom_match else 0\n                print(f\"   Initial Zoom: {initial_zoom}\")\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"   Warning: {e}\")\n            initial_zoom = 0\n        \n        # 5. Test Zoom-Out button\n        print(\"\\n5. Testing Zoom-Out button...\")\n        try:\n            zoom_out_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"焦距-\")')\n            if zoom_out_btn.count() > 0:\n                print(\"   Clicking Zoom-Out...\")\n                zoom_out_btn.click()\n                page.wait_for_timeout(2000)  # Wait for movement\n                \n                # Stop movement (release button effect)\n                # In real UI, user would release mouse - simulate by clicking stop or center\n                center_btn = page.locator('.ptz-btn.center')\n                if center_btn.count() > 0:\n                    center_btn.click()\n                    page.wait_for_timeout(500)\n                \n                # Get new position\n                page.wait_for_timeout(1000)\n                new_pos = page.locator('#ptzPosition').text_content()\n                print(f\"   After Zoom-Out: {new_pos}\")\n                \n                zoom_match = re.search(r'Zoom:\\s*(\\d+)', new_pos)\n                new_zoom = int(zoom_match.group(1)) if zoom_match else 0\n                print(f\"   New Zoom: {new_zoom}\")\n                \n                if new_zoom != initial_zoom:\n                    print(f\"   PASS: Zoom changed from {initial_zoom} to {new_zoom}\")\n                else:\n                    print(f\"   FAIL: Zoom unchanged ({initial_zoom})\")\n            else:\n                print(\"   ERROR: Zoom-Out button not found\")\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"   ERROR: {e}\")\n        \n        # 6. Test Zoom-In button\n        print(\"\\n6. Testing Zoom-In button...\")\n        try:\n            zoom_in_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"焦距+\")')\n            if zoom_in_btn.count() > 0:\n                print(\"   Clicking Zoom-In...\")\n                zoom_in_btn.click()\n                page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n                \n                center_btn = page.locator('.ptz-btn.center')\n                if center_btn.count() > 0:\n                    center_btn.click()\n                    page.wait_for_timeout(500)\n                \n                page.wait_for_timeout(1000)\n                final_pos = page.locator('#ptzPosition').text_content()\n                print(f\"   After Zoom-