{"type":"message","id":"25b2a9b9","parentId":"d2d7e4a7","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:16:48.541Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**关键发现**：Zoom 和 Focus 按钮使用的是 `onmousedown` 事件，而不是 `onclick`！\n\n**这意味着**：\n1. `onmousedown` 在鼠标按下时触发，发送**开始移动**指令\n2. 用户需要**按住按钮**一段时间，让镜头移动\n3. 松开鼠标时，需要触发 `onmouseup` 来**停止移动**\n\n但当前代码中只有 `onmousedown`，没有对应的 `onmouseup` 调用 `ptzStop()`！\n\n让我检查是否有全局的 mouseup 处理："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_41b790ce885f4a7ca4a458fc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Select-String -Path \"src/web/index.html\" -Pattern \"mouseup|touchend|ptzStop\" -Context 0,2 | Select-Object -First 20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":157384,"output":184,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":157568,"cost":{"input":0.157384,"output":0.0005888,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1579728}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781201798876,"responseId":"cht000d3952@dx19eb7e6895bb894142"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3fb4f480","parentId":"25b2a9b9","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:16:49.045Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_41b790ce885f4a7ca4a458fc","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"> src\\web\\index.html:228:            init[7mMouseUp[0m();[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:229:            refreshDevices();[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:230:            addLog('info', 'AstroHub ������');[0m\r\n> src\\web\\index.html:992:        function init[7mMouseUp[0m() {\r\n> src\\web\\index.html:993:            document.addEventListener('[7mmouseup[0m', function() { ptzStop(); });\r\n> src\\web\\index.html:994:            document.addEventListener('[7mtouchend[0m', function() { ptzStop(); });[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:995:        }[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:996:        // Clock[0m\r\n> src\\web\\index.html:1453:        function [7mptzStop[0m() {[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:1454:            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:1455:            if (!dev) return;[0m\r\n> src\\web\\index.html:2031:            ptzMove, ptzHome, [7mptzStop[0m, getPtzPosition, onPtzDeviceChange,[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:2032:            calibrate, saveSettings,[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:2033:            funcDetectRun, funcDetectRestore,[0m"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":401,"aggregated":"> src\\web\\index.html:228:            init[7mMouseUp[0m();[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:229:            refreshDevices();[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:230:            addLog('info', 'AstroHub ������');[0m\r\n> src\\web\\index.html:992:        function init[7mMouseUp[0m() {\r\n> src\\web\\index.html:993:            document.addEventListener('[7mmouseup[0m', function() { ptzStop(); });\r\n> src\\web\\index.html:994:            document.addEventListener('[7mtouchend[0m', function() { ptzStop(); });[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:995:        }[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:996:        // Clock[0m\r\n> src\\web\\index.html:1453:        function [7mptzStop[0m() {[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:1454:            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:1455:            if (!dev) return;[0m\r\n> src\\web\\index.html:2031:            ptzMove, ptzHome, [7mptzStop[0m, getPtzPosition, onPtzDeviceChange,[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:2032:            calibrate, saveSettings,[0m\r\n[7m[0m  src\\web\\index.html:2033:            funcDetectRun, funcDetectRestore,[0m","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781201809045}}
{"type":"message","id":"0400e0ba","parentId":"3fb4f480","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:17:11.562Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"有全局 mouseup 处理！`initMouseUp()` 在全局注册了 `mouseup` 和 `touchend` 事件，自动调用 `ptzStop()`。\n\n所以逻辑应该是：\n1. 用户按下按钮 → `onmousedown` → 开始移动\n2. 用户松开鼠标 → `mouseup` 事件 → `ptzStop()` → 停止移动\n\n但 Playwright 的 `click()` 方法太快了，可能：\n- 点击 → 松开 → 停止，整个过程只有几毫秒\n- 移动指令发送后立刻被停止指令覆盖\n\n让我修改测试，使用 `page.mouse.down()` 和等待后再 `page.mouse.up()`："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-7a97c0de61e54a9dbc0dc024b875ea21","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nv5.47 E2E Test - Simulate real mouse hold behavior\n\"\"\"\nimport time\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\n\nBASE_URL = \"http://localhost:10280\"\nDEVICE_IP = \"192.168.5.72\"\n\ndef test_zoom_with_hold():\n    with sync_playwright() as p:\n        browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True)\n        context = browser.new_context()\n        page = context.new_page()\n        \n        print(\"=\" * 60)\n        print(\"Zoom Test with Mouse Hold Simulation\")\n        print(\"=\" * 60)\n        \n        # Open and navigate to console\n        page.goto(BASE_URL, timeout=30000)\n        page.wait_for_load_state('networkidle')\n        \n        console_btn = page.locator('[data-page=\"console\"]')\n        console_btn.click()\n        page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n        \n        # Get initial zoom\n        position_div = page.locator('#ptzPosition')\n        initial_pos = position_div.text_content()\n        print(f\"\\nInitial position: {initial_pos}\")\n        \n        import re\n        zoom_match = re.search(r'Zoom:\\s*(\\d+)', initial_pos)\n        initial_zoom = int(zoom_match.group(1)) if zoom_match else 0\n        print(f\"Initial Zoom: {initial_zoom}\")\n        \n        # Find zoom-out button\n        zoom_out_btn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"焦距-\")')\n        if zoom_out_btn.count() == 0:\n            print(\"ERROR: Zoom-Out button not found\")\n            browser.close()\n            return\n        \n        # Get button position\n        btn_box = zoom_out_btn.bounding_box()\n        if not btn_box:\n            print(\"ERROR: Cannot get button position\")\n            browser.close()\n            return\n        \n        btn_x = btn_box['x'] + btn_box['width'] / 2\n        btn_y = btn_box['y'] + btn_box['height'] / 2\n        \n        print(f\"\\nButton position: ({btn_x}, {btn_y})\")\n        \n        # Simulate real mouse hold: press, hold 2 seconds, release\n        print(\"\\nSimulating mouse hold for 2 seconds...\")\n        \n        # Move mouse to button\n        page.mouse.move(btn_x, btn_y)\n        \n        # Press and hold\n        page.mouse.down()\n        print(\"  Mouse pressed - Zoom-Out started\")\n        \n        # Hold for 2 seconds (let the device move)\n        page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n        \n        # Release\n        page.mouse.up()\n        print(\"  Mouse released - Zoom-Out stopped\")\n        \n        # Wait for position update\n        page.wait_for_timeout(1000)\n        \n        # Get new position\n        new_pos = position_div.text_content()\n        print(f\"\\nNew position: {new_pos}\")\n        \n        zoom_match = re.search(r'Zoom:\\s*(\\d+)', new_pos)\n        new_zoom = int(zoom_match.group(1)) if zoom_match else 0\n        print(f\"New Zoom: {new_zoom}\")\n        \n        if new_zoom != initial_zoom:\n            print(f\"\\nPASS: Zoom changed from {initial_zoom} to {new_zoom}\")\n        else:\n            print(f\"\\nFAIL: Zoom unchanged ({initial_zoom})\")\n        \n        browser.close()\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    test_zoom_with_hold()","path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/tests/e2e_zoom_hold.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":153046,"output":874,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":153920,"cost":{"input":0.153046,"output":0.0027968000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.15584279999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781201809048,"responseId":"cht000d41fa@dx19eb7e6b3fcb9ca102"}}
