{"type":"message","id":"c9ed8d46","parentId":"071024e3","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:24:40.501Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2cf2dc6325524ff7aa6ef523","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Calling ptzZoom('out') ===\r\nResult: None\r\n\r\n=== Network Requests ===\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/devices/192.168.5.72/credentials\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/position\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/presets\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/position\r\n  POST http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/stop\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/position\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/position\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/position\r\n  POST http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/move\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/position\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/position\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/position\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/position\r\n\r\n=== Position ===\r\n  Pan: 1595 | Tilt: 432 | Zoom: 82\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"nova-breeze","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"=== Calling ptzZoom('out') ===\r\nResult: None\r\n\r\n=== Network Requests ===\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/devices/192.168.5.72/credentials\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/position\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/presets\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/position\r\n  POST http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/stop\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/position\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/position\r\n  GET http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/position\r\n  POST http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/mo