{"type":"message","id":"eef39f35","parentId":"c9ed8d46","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:24:58.825Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**发现关键问题！**\n\n网络请求显示：\n1. `POST .../stop` 在 `POST .../move` **之前**！\n2. 顺序是：stop → move → position updates\n\n这说明：\n- `ptzZoom('out')` 被调用，发送 `move` 请求\n- 但全局 `mouseup` 事件处理立即触发了 `ptzStop()`\n- `stop` 请求在 `move` 之前到达后端（因为 Playwright 自动释放鼠标）\n\n**根本原因**：Playwright 的 `page.evaluate()` 会触发浏览器的某些事件，可能触发了 mouseup。\n\n而且看到 **Zoom 已经变成了 82**！说明功能是正常的，只是时机问题。\n\n让我再次测试，这次手动触发函数并等待："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-ae0dddae9b3346268e768e7a4b20fbab","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nE2E Test - Verify Zoom actually works\n\"\"\"\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\nimport time\n\nBASE_URL = \"http://localhost:10280\"\n\ndef test_zoom_works():\n    with sync_playwright() as p:\n        browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True)\n        context = browser.new_context()\n        page = context.new_page()\n        \n        page.goto(BASE_URL, timeout=30000)\n        page.wait_for_load_state('networkidle')\n        \n        console_btn = page.locator('[data-page=\"console\"]')\n        console_btn.click()\n        page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n        \n        # Get initial zoom\n        import re\n        pos = page.evaluate(\"() => document.getElementById('ptzPosition')?.textContent\")\n        zoom_match = re.search(r'Zoom:\\s*(\\d+)', pos)\n        initial_zoom = int(zoom_match.group(1)) if zoom_match else 0\n        print(f\"Initial Zoom: {initial_zoom}\")\n        \n        # Use API directly via evaluate (bypass mouse events)\n        print(\"\\nSending zoom-out via API...\")\n        page.evaluate(\"\"\"\n            () => {\n                return fetch('http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/move', {\n                    method: 'POST',\n                    headers: {'Content-Type': 'application/json'},\n                    body: JSON.stringify({direction: 'zoom-out', speed: 80})\n                }).then(r => r.json());\n            }\n        \"\"\")\n        \n        # Wait 2 seconds for movement\n        page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n        \n        # Send stop\n        print(\"Sending stop...\")\n        page.evaluate(\"\"\"\n            () => {\n                return fetch('http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/stop', {\n                    method: 'POST'\n                }).then(r => r.json());\n            }\n        \"\"\")\n        \n        page.wait_for_timeout(1000)\n        \n        # Get new zoom\n        pos = page.evaluate(\"() => document.getElementById('ptzPosition')?.textContent\")\n        zoom_match = re.search(r'Zoom:\\s*(\\d+)', pos)\n        new_zoom = int(zoom_match.group(1)) if zoom_match else 0\n        print(f\"New Zoom: {new_zoom}\")\n        \n        if new_zoom != initial_zoom:\n            print(f\"\\nPASS: Zoom changed from {initial_zoom} to {new_zoom}\")\n        else:\n            print(f\"\\nFAIL: Zoom unchanged ({initial_zoom})\")\n        \n        browser.close()\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    test_zoom_works()","path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/tests/e2e_zoom_api.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":51416,"output":741,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52157,"cost":{"input":0.051415999999999996,"output":0.0023712000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.05378719999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781202280502,"responseId":"cht000d8760@dx19eb7ede5c1b9cb212"}}
