{"type":"message","id":"a712a3a2","parentId":"074e8f2d","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:25:29.888Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 结论\n\n**Zoom 功能正常！** 问题在于：\n1. Playwright 的 `page.evaluate()` 触发了全局 `mouseup` 事件\n2. `mouseup` 调用 `ptzStop()`，抵消了 `move` 指令\n\n**实际问题**：前端 `ptzZoom` 函数中，`apiPost` 返回 Promise 后，`.then()` 和 `.catch()` 是异步处理，但 `ptzStop()` 由全局 `mouseup` 触发，可能过早停止移动。\n\n让我测试真实用户操作（用 `dispatchEvent` 模拟）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2e46a3202576439ea2c0310b","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nE2E Test - Simulate real button click with event dispatch\n\"\"\"\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\nimport re\n\nBASE_URL = \"http://localhost:10280\"\n\ndef test_button_click():\n    with sync_playwright() as p:\n        browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True)\n        context = browser.new_context()\n        page = context.new_page()\n        \n        page.goto(BASE_URL, timeout=30000)\n        page.wait_for_load_state('networkidle')\n        \n        console_btn = page.locator('[data-page=\"console\"]')\n        console_btn.click()\n        page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n        \n        # Get initial zoom\n        pos = page.evaluate(\"() => document.getElementById('ptzPosition')?.textContent\")\n        zoom_match = re.search(r'Zoom:\\s*(\\d+)', pos)\n        initial_zoom = int(zoom_match.group(1)) if zoom_match else 0\n        print(f\"Initial Zoom: {initial_zoom}\")\n        \n        # Find zoom-out button and dispatch events\n        print(\"\\nSimulating button press...\")\n        \n        # Use dispatchEvent to avoid Playwright's auto-mouseup behavior\n        page.evaluate(\"\"\"\n            () => {\n                const btn = document.querySelector('button[onmousedown*=\"ptzZoom(\\\\'out\\\\')\"]');\n                if (btn) {\n                    // Dispatch mousedown\n                    btn.dispatchEvent(new MouseEvent('mousedown', {bubbles: true}));\n                    console.log('mousedown dispatched');\n                }\n            }\n        \"\"\")\n        \n        # Wait for movement\n        page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n        \n        # Dispatch mouseup to stop\n        print(\"Simulating button release...\")\n        page.evaluate(\"\"\"\n            () => {\n                document.dispatchEvent(new MouseEvent('mouseup', {bubbles: true}));\n            }\n        \"\"\")\n        \n        page.wait_for_timeout(1000)\n        \n        # Get new zoom\n        pos = page.evaluate(\"() => document.getElementById('ptzPosition')?.textContent\")\n        zoom_match = re.search(r'Zoom:\\s*(\\d+)', pos)\n        new_zoom = int(zoom_match.group(1)) if zoom_match else 0\n        print(f\"New Zoom: {new_zoom}\")\n        \n        if new_zoom != initial_zoom:\n            print(f\"\\nPASS: Zoom changed from {initial_zoom} to {new_zoom}\")\n        else:\n            print(f\"\\nFAIL: Zoom unchanged ({initial_zoom})\")\n        \n        browser.close()\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    test_button_click()","path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/tests/e2e_button_dispatch.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":52541,"output":679,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53220,"cost":{"input":0.052541,"output":0.0021728000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0547138}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781202321453,"responseId":"cht000db600@dx19eb7ee89f6b87f702"}}
