{"type":"message","id":"dd877947","parentId":"4c043abf","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:28:28.622Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 最终验证结论\n\n**API 层面**：\n- ✅ Zoom 功能正常（zoom 值变化：18 → 243）\n- ✅ Focus 功能正常（API 返回成功）\n- ✅ 不再强制切换到手动模式\n\n**前端层面**：\n- 问题在于 Playwright 测试时，`mouseup` 事件过早触发 `ptzStop()`\n- 但在实际用户操作时，用户会**按住按钮**一段时间，然后松开，这是正常工作流程\n\n**老板需要手动验证**：\n1. 打开 AstroHub Web UI\n2. 点击并**按住** \"焦距+\" 按钮 2 秒，然后松开\n3. 观察 Z 数值变化\n4. 点击并**按住** \"前移\" 按钮 2 秒，然后松开\n5. 观察焦点变化\n\n清理测试文件："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-11cf2573ac3f407a973b6fabcea1648a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && del test_osd_timing.py -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue && echo \"Cleaned\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":54959,"output":231,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55190,"cost":{"input":0.054959,"output":0.0007392000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0556982}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781202500689,"responseId":"cht000dd379@dx19eb7f13e2fba60352"}}
