{"type":"message","id":"e6b705d6","parentId":"6390af80","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:28:41.132Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## v5.47 修复汇报\n\n**已修复**：\n1. ✅ **Zoom 按钮**：添加 `.then()` 处理成功响应，显示操作日志\n2. ✅ **Focus 按钮**：移除强制切换手动模式的逻辑，直接发送 focus 移动指令\n3. ✅ **API 验证**：Zoom 功能正常（zoom 值变化），Focus 功能正常\n\n**OSD Info 延迟**：\n- 海康设备处理 VideoOverlay PUT 需要 2-3 秒\n- 这是设备固有特性，无法通过代码优化\n\n**老板需手动验证**：\n- 打开 AstroHub，点击并**按住**焦距/对焦按钮 1-2 秒后松开\n- 观察 Z 数值变化和焦点变化"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":55387,"output":169,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55556,"cost":{"input":0.055387,"output":0.0005408,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0559278}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781202509171,"responseId":"cht000dcf7b@dx19eb7f171e6ba5d322"}}
