{"type":"message","id":"e21b5c9d","parentId":"94acf325","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:32:23.298Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`ptzMove` 和 `ptzZoom` 结构相同。问题在于 **`ptzStop` 被 `mouseup` 触发时，move 请求可能还没发送出去**。\n\n**根本问题**：`apiPost` 是 async 函数，返回 Promise。`mousedown` 触发 `ptzZoom('out')` 后，`apiPost` 开始执行（异步），但 `mouseup` 立即触发 `ptzStop()`，而 `ptzStop()` 也是一个 async 函数。\n\n如果 `ptzStop()` 的请求先到达后端，设备就不会移动。\n\n**修复方案**：在 `ptzZoom` 和 `ptzFocus` 中，等待 `apiPost` 完成后再返回。但这需要改为 async/await 模式。\n\n或者更简单：**阻止全局 mouseup 在 zoom/focus 按钮上触发 stop**。\n\n检查按钮是否阻止了事件冒泡："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e92bead0741e41779fe4c213","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":10,"offset":68,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":60752,"output":239,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60991,"cost":{"input":0.060752,"output":0.0007648,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0615168}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781202730522,"responseId":"cht000dc041@dx19eb7f4e1e0b85e102"}}
{"type":"message","id":"49505a41","parentId":"e21b5c9d","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:32:23.307Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e92bead0741e41779fe4c213","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px\">焦距:</span>\r\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('in')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('in')\">🔍+ 焦距+</button>\r\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('out')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('out')\">🔍- 焦距-</button>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin-bottom:12px\">\r\n                            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px\">对焦:</span>\r\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('near')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('near')\">🔧- 前移</button>\r\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('far')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('far')\">🔧+ 后移</button>\r\n                            <select id=\"focusMode\" style=\"padding:4px 8px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"setFocusMode(this.value)\">\r\n                                <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\r\n\n[115 more lines in file. Use offset=78 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781202743307}}
{"type":"message","id":"9f060196","parentId":"49505a41","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:32:28.994Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"按钮没有阻止事件冒泡。`mousedown` 事件会冒泡到 document，然后 `mouseup` 也会触发全局的 `ptzStop()`。\n\n**修复**：在 `ptzZoom` 和 `ptzFocus` 函数中设置一个标志，阻止 `ptzStop()` 执行。\n\n修改 `index.html`："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-77231daef07a4f75bf2c9a649dd6365e","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":990,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":61126,"output":112,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61238,"cost":{"input":0.061126,"output":0.00035840000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0614844}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781202743308,"responseId":"cht000dc0dc@dx19eb7f4f23eb85e102"}}
