{"type":"message","id":"e79063e5","parentId":"4ae1d190","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:33:53.463Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_478cf920729b4a1baca052d0","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Loading page...\r\n2. Opening Console...\r\n   Status: 4k 32X DC\r\n\r\n3. Testing Zoom-Out (hold 2s)...\r\n   Zoom before: 243\r\n   Zoom after:  243\r\n\r\n4. Testing Zoom-In (hold 2s)...\r\n   Zoom after:  243\r\n\r\n5. Testing Focus Near (hold 2s)...\r\n   Focus mode before: manual\r\n   Focus mode after:  manual\r\n\r\n6. Testing Focus Far (hold 2s)...\r\n\r\n7. Testing PTZ OSD toggle...\r\n\r\n8. Testing OSD Info toggle...\r\n\r\n9. Checking JS errors...\r\n\r\n============================================================\r\nSUMMARY\r\n============================================================\r\n  [FAIL] Zoom-Out: 243 -> 243\r\n  [FAIL] Zoom-In: 243 -> 243\r\n  [PASS] Focus Near: mode preserved=True (manual -> manual)\r\n  [PASS] Focus Far: mode preserved=True (manual -> manual)\r\n  [PASS] PTZ OSD: toggle time: 1.1s\r\n  [PASS] OSD Info Off: time: 4.0s\r\n  [PASS] OSD Info On: time: 4.0s\r\n  [PASS] JS Errors: no errors\r\n\r\nTotal: 8 | Pass: 6 | Fail: 2\n\nProcess exited with code 1."}],"details":{"status":"failed","sessionId":"mellow-trail","exitCode":1,"aggregated":"1. Loading page...\r\n2. Opening Console...\r\n   Status: 4k 32X DC\r\n\r\n3. Testing Zoom-Out (hold 2s)...\r\n   Zoom before: 243\r\n   Zoom after:  243\r\n\r\n4. Testing Zoom-In (hold 2s)...\r\n   Zoom after:  243\r\n\r\n5. Testing Focus Near (hold 2s)...\r\n   Focus mode before: manual\r\n   Focus mode after:  manual\r\n\r\n6. Testing Focus Far (hold 2s)...\r\n\r\n7. Testing PTZ OSD toggle...\r\n\r\n8. Testing OSD Info toggle...\r\n\r\n9. Checking JS errors...\r\n\r\n============================================================\r\nSUMMARY\r\n============================================================\r\n  [FAIL] Zoom-Out: 243 -> 243\r\n  [FAIL] Zoom-In: 243 -> 243