{"type":"message","id":"0eed83a6","parentId":"512ada60","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:35:46.004Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3d3c12329b304fddbbc8f5ed","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function ptzStop() {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n            if (!dev) return;\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/stop', null).catch(function(e) {});\r\n        }\r\n        function getPtzPosition() {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n            if (!dev) return;\r\n            apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/position').then(function(result) {\r\n                var posEl = document.getElementById('ptzPosition');\r\n                if (result && result.success && result.data) {\r\n                    var p = result.data;\r\n                    posEl.innerHTML = 'Pan: ' + (p.pan || 0) + ' | Tilt: ' + (p.tilt || 0) + ' | Zoom: ' + (p.zoom || 0);\r\n                } else {\r\n                    posEl.innerHTML = 'Pan: -- | Tilt: -- | Zoom: --';\r\n                }\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {});\r\n        }\r\n        // Calibration (placeholder)\r\n        function calibrate(type) {\r\n\n[1053 more lines in file. Use offset=1473 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781202946004}}
{"type":"message","id":"41467354","parentId":"0eed83a6","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:35:55.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`ptzStop` 直接调用 `apiPost`。问题可能是全局 mouseup 处理器在页面加载时立即绑定，并且某些 Playwright 操作触发了 mouseup。\n\n让我检查 `initMouseUp` 是否在某个时候被调用："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-fcd9d8a8fcd7470f8fe79a04869d6095","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nDebug - Check mouseup listeners\n\"\"\"\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\n\nBASE = \"http://localhost:10280\"\n\ndef test():\n    with sync_playwright() as p:\n        browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True)\n        page = browser.new_page()\n        \n        page.goto(BASE)\n        page.wait_for_load_state('networkidle')\n        page.click('[data-page=\"console\"]')\n        page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n        \n        # Check if mouseup listener is registered\n        info = page.evaluate(\"\"\"() => {\n            // Try to get event listeners (not available in regular browser)\n            const listeners = window.getEventListeners ? window.getEventListeners(document) : 'not available';\n            \n            // Check if initMouseUp was called\n            return {\n                listeners: listeners,\n                hasInitMouseUp: typeof initMouseUp === 'function',\n                documentHasMouseUp: document.onmouseup !== null\n            };\n        }\"\"\")\n        \n        print(f\"Mouseup info: {info}\")\n        \n        browser.close()\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    test()","path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/tests/e2e_mouseup_info.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":67374,"output":314,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67688,"cost":{"input":0.067374,"output":0.0010048000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0683788}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781202946005,"responseId":"cht000edc06@dx19eb7f80949b893102"}}
