{"type":"message","id":"4ffbb815","parentId":"7b8f0fa5","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:43:17.681Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Zoom 仍然失败**。`dispatchEvent` 方式发送 `mousedown` 后，`ptzZoom` 函数被调用了，但 zoom 值没变。\n\n问题可能是：`ptzZoom` 函数发送 `apiPost` 请求，但 `mouseup` 事件立即触发 `ptzStop()`，两者几乎同时发送，stop 可能在 move 之前到达。\n\n让我检查 `ptzMove` 函数（方向按钮用的）是如何工作的："}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781203397656}}
{"type":"message","id":"d1865e46","parentId":"4ffbb815","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:43:18.231Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`ptzMove` 和 `ptzZoom` 结构相同。问题在于 **`ptzStop` 被 `mouseup` 触发时，move 请求可能还没发送出去**。\n\n**根本问题**：`apiPost` 是 async 函数，返回 Promise。`mousedown` 触发 `ptzZoom('out')` 后，`apiPost` 开始执行（异步），但 `mouseup` 立即触发 `ptzStop()`，而 `ptzStop()` 也是一个 async 函数。\n\n如果 `ptzStop()` 的请求先到达后端，设备就不会移动。\n\n**修复方案**：在 `ptzZoom` 和 `ptzFocus` 中，等待 `apiPost` 完成后再返回。但这需要改为 async/await 模式。\n\n或者更简单：**阻止全局 mouseup 在 zoom/focus 按钮上触发 stop**。\n\n检查按钮是否阻止了事件冒泡："}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781203398208}}
