{"type":"message","id":"8cccd82c","parentId":"587d4e1c","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:47:37.500Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Zoom-In 成功了！** 从 10 变成 41。\n\nZoom-Out 失败是因为 zoom 已经是最小值 10，无法再缩小。\n\n## v5.47 修复完成\n\n**修复内容**：\n1. ✅ **Zoom 速度缩放问题**：移除重复缩放，直接传递 speed 值\n2. ✅ **Focus 速度缩放问题**：同样修复\n3. ✅ **Focus 模式保持**：不再强制切换到手动模式\n4. ✅ **按钮事件处理**：添加 `onmouseup` 直接触发 `ptzStop()`\n\n**测试结果**：\n| 功能 | 结果 |\n|------|------|\n| Zoom-In | ✅ PASS (10→41) |\n| Zoom-Out | ⚠️ 已达最小值，无法再缩小 |\n| Focus Near | ✅ PASS (模式保持) |\n| Focus Far | ✅ PASS (模式保持) |\n| PTZ OSD | ✅ PASS |\n| OSD Info | ✅ PASS (~4秒) |\n\n**OSD Info 4 秒延迟**：海康设备处理 VideoOverlay PUT 的固有特性。"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781203657480}}
