{"type":"message","id":"eb4442af","parentId":"79c37b03","timestamp":"2026-06-11T18:54:18.287Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 结论\n\n**海康 ISAPI 没有公开的焦点位置读取接口。**\n\n检查结果：\n- `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/focusConfiguration` - 只有模式（auto/manual/semiautomatic）和限制值，**无位置**\n- `/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/status` - 只有 pan/tilt/zoom，**无 focus**\n- `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/focusStatus` - 404\n- `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/focusPosition` - 404\n- `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/lensStatus` - 404\n\n**Focus 操作特点**：\n- 海康 ISAPI 支持 **continuous focus move**（连续对焦移动），通过 `<focus>` 速度值控制\n- 但 **不提供焦点位置的绝对数值读取**\n- Focus 操作是\"盲操作\"，只能通过画面清晰度判断效果\n\n这与 Zoom 不同：\n- Zoom 有 `absoluteZoom` 数值（10-320）\n- Focus 没有对应的 `absoluteFocus` 数值"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":91485,"output":228,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91713,"cost":{"input":0.091485,"output":0.0007296000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0922146}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781204048911,"responseId":"cht000e8d7b@dx19eb808e2c9b893102"}}
