</TimeTaskList>\r\n<TrackInitPosition>\r\n<slaveCameraID min=\"1\" max=\"1\"/>\r\n</TrackInitPosition>\r\n<LockPT>false</LockPT>\r\n<isSupportPTZEagleFocusing>true</isSupportPTZEagleFocusing>\r\n<LFPositionCap>\r\n<elevation min=\"-900\" max=\"2700\">0</elevation>\r\n<azimuth min=\"0\" max=\"3600\">0</azimuth>\r\n<absoluteZoom min=\"1\" max=\"1000\">0</absoluteZoom>\r\n</LFPositionCap>\r\n<isSupportManualWiper>true</isSupportManualWiper>\r\n<PTZAuxType opt=\"LIGHT,FAN,HEATER\"/>\r\n<isSupportGPSCtrl>true</isSupportGPSCtrl>\r\n<isSupportGyroVerify>true</isSupportGyroVerify>\r\n</PTZChanelCap>","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781204537450}}
{"type":"message","id":"86fa8297","parentId":"2d2a44a5","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:02:25.144Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**发现关键信息！**\n\n从 capabilities 中看到：\n- `ContinuousPanTiltSpace`: X/Y 范围 **-100 到 100**\n- `ContinuousZoomSpace`: Z 范围 **-100 到 100**\n- **没有 `ContinuousFocusSpace`！**\n\n这说明该设备 **不支持通过 PTZ continuous 接口控制 focus**！\n\n但之前我测试 `focus=10` 返回了 OK。让我查看 AstroHub 代码中的设置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7a416f98f2c8468caf400dfa","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1062,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/core/ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":106048,"output":144,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106192,"cost":{"input":0.10604799999999999,"output":0.00046080000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.10650879999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781204537452,"responseId":"cht000de191@dx19eb81052d6ba5b442"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b2954d1e","parentId":"86fa8297","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:02:25.151Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7a416f98f2c8468caf400dfa","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def continuous_move(self, pan: float = 0, tilt: float = 0, zoom: float = 0, focus: float = 0) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"连续移动 PTZ。\r\n\r\n        ISAPI 2.0 格式: panSpeed/tiltSpeed 范围 -10(left/down) 到 10(right/up),\r\n        zoomSpeed -10(out) 到 10(in), focusSpeed -10(near) 到 10(far), 0 = stop.\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        # 将 0-100 范围映射到 -10..10 (ISAPI 2.0 规范)\r\n        pan_speed = round(pan / 10.0)\r\n        tilt_speed = round(tilt / 10.0)\r\n        zoom_speed = round(zoom / 10.0)\r\n        focus_speed = round(focus / 10.0)\r\n\r\n        # 停止移动：使用 /continuous 端点速度全0\r\n        if pan_speed == 0 and tilt_speed == 0 and zoom_speed == 0 and focus_speed == 0:\r\n            xml = '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>'\r\n            xml += '<PTZData version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">'\r\n            xml += '<ptzSpeed>'\r\n            xml += '<pan>0</pan><tilt>0</tilt><zoom>0</zoom><focus>0</focus>'\r\n            xml += '</ptzSpeed></PTZData>'\r\n            result = self.client.put(f\"{self._ptz_base()}/continuous\", xml)\r\n            return result.status_code == 200\r\n\r\n        xml = f\"\"\"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<PTZData version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n  <ptzSpeed>\r\n    <pan>{pan_speed}</pan>\r\n    <tilt>{tilt_speed}</tilt>\r\n    <zoom>{zoom_speed}</zoom>\r\n    <focus>{focus_speed}</focus>\r\n  </ptzSpeed>\r\n\n[1600 more lines in file. Use offset=1092 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781204545151}}
{"type":"message","id":"df8d8b05","parentId":"b2954d1e","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:02:35.433Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 总结\n\n**海康 ISAPI Focus 参数说明**：\n\n| 参数 | 说明 | 范围 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `focusStyle` | 对焦模式 | auto / manual / semiautomatic |\n| `focusLimited` | 对焦限制值 | 300 (设备返回) |\n| `focusSpeed` | 连续对焦速度 | **-10 到 10** (ISAPI 2.0 规范) |\n\n**关键发现**：\n1. **该设备不支持通过 PTZ continuous 接口控制 focus**（capabilities 中没有 `ContinuousFocusSpace`）\n2. 但 ISAPI 接口仍然接受 `<focus>` 参数（返回 OK）\n3. 实际 focus 控制可能需要通过 **Image/channels/1/focusConfiguration** 端点\n\n**AstroHub 当前设置**：\n- `focus_speed` 范围：**-10 到 10**（ISAPI 2.0 规范）\n- 用户输入 speed 0-100，映射到 -10~10\n\n**问题**：虽然 ISAPI 返回 OK，但设备可能没有实际执行 focus 移动。需要通过其他方式验证或使用不同的 ISAPI 端点。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":106747,"output":264,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107011,"cost":{"input":0.106747,"output":0.0008448,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1075918}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781204545154,"responseId":"cht000de2a3@dx19eb810707eba5b442"}}
