{"type":"message","id":"b1937f31","parentId":"7a5f6db7","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:12:40.502Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"API 调用成功。\n\n## v5.47 修复汇报\n\n**Focus 控制说明**：\n\n| 项目 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| ISAPI 端点 | `/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/continuous` |\n| 参数 | `<focus>` 速度值，范围 -10 到 10 |\n| 设备支持 | `isSupportPTZEagleFocusing=true` 但无 `ContinuousFocusSpace` |\n| 实际效果 | ISAPI 接受请求但设备可能不执行 |\n\n**海康官方文档中 focusPos 参数**：\n- 端点：`/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/focusConfiguration`\n- 参数：`<focusPos>` 绝对位置（0-1000）\n- 限制：无法读取当前 focusPos 值\n\n**修复状态**：\n- ✅ Zoom 功能已修复（速度缩放问题）\n- ✅ Focus API 调用正常\n- ⚠️ Focus 实际效果需老板通过画面验证"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":109123,"output":221,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109344,"cost":{"input":0.109123,"output":0.0007072000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1098302}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781205149277,"responseId":"cht000d31e1@dx19eb819b120b85e102"}}
