{"type":"message","id":"5e5f744f","parentId":"b94edd8b","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:13:20.647Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到。\n\n## v5.47 最终总结\n\n**已修复**：\n| 功能 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Zoom 速度缩放 | ✅ 已修复 | 移除重复缩放，直接传递 speed |\n| Zoom API | ✅ 正常 | zoom 值变化正常 |\n| Focus API | ✅ 正常 | ISAPI 返回 OK |\n| Focus 模式保持 | ✅ 已修复 | 不再强制切换到手动模式 |\n| OSD PTZ | ✅ 正常 | 响应 ~300ms |\n| OSD Info | ⚠️ 设备特性 | 响应 ~4秒（设备固有） |\n\n**Focus 说明**：\n- 海康 ISAPI 接口接受 `<focus>` 参数，但设备可能不执行连续对焦\n- `focusPos` 绝对位置控制需要手动模式，但无法读取当前位置\n- **老板需要通过实际画面验证 Focus 是否有效**\n\n**备份位置**: `backup_20260612_022908`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":103830,"output":220,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104050,"cost":{"input":0.10382999999999999,"output":0.0007040000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.10453399999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781205184603,"responseId":"cht000d4e80@dx19eb81a335db85f582"}}
