{"type":"message","id":"ba1a3a84","parentId":"887d27f9","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:18:38.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"成功登录并进入预览页面。但没有捕获到 focus 相关的请求。\n\n让我查看截图并分析页面结构："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-791186a0e7ea4d3191f9329a8d22eb48","name":"image","arguments":{"image":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/hikvision_ptz.png","prompt":"分析这个海康摄像头 Web 界面截图，找出：\n1. 页面上是否有 PTZ 控制面板？\n2. 是否有 Focus（对焦）控制按钮？\n3. 控制按钮的位置和标签是什么？\n4. 是否有 Zoom 控制按钮？"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":108115,"output":117,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108232,"cost":{"input":0.10811499999999999,"output":0.00037440000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.10848939999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781205509625,"responseId":"cht000d7f56@dx19eb81f27aeba5e412"}}
