{"type":"message","id":"8a9be6d6","parentId":"959155d3","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:20:25.793Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**找到官方 Focus 控制方法了！**\n\n## 关键发现\n\n**海康官方 Focus ISAPI 端点**：\n```\nPUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus\n```\n\n**请求格式**：\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<FocusData>\n  <focus>-60</focus>\n</FocusData>\n```\n\n**参数说明**：\n- `<focus>` 速度值，**负数表示前移（近焦），正数表示后移（远焦）**\n- 示例：`-60` 表示焦点前移速度 60，`0` 表示停止\n\n这是 **不同于 PTZ continuous 接口** 的独立 Focus 控制端点！\n\n现在修复 AstroHub："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_de2c6d61bb7e454c97041918","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def focus_move_continuous(self, direction: str, speed: int = 50) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"连续对焦移动 - 通过官方 Focus 端点。\n\n        direction: 'near' (前移/近焦) 或 'far' (后移/远焦)\n        speed: 0-100\n        \"\"\"\n        endpoint = f\"/System/Video/inputs/channels/{self.channel}/focus\"\n        \n        # focus 速度范围约 -100 到 100\n        # near (前移) 负值，far (后移) 正值\n        focus_speed = speed\n        if direction == 'near':\n            focus_speed = -speed\n        \n        xml = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<FocusData>\n  <focus>{focus_speed}</focus>\n</FocusData>'''\n        \n        result = self.client.put(endpoint, xml)\n        return result.status_code == 200\n\n    def focus_stop(self) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"停止对焦移动。\"\"\"\n        endpoint = f\"/System/Video/inputs/channels/{self.channel}/focus\"\n        xml = '''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<FocusData>\n  <focus>0</focus>\n</FocusData>'''\n        result = self.client.put(endpoint, xml)\n        return result.status_code == 200\n","oldText":"    def focus_move_continuous(self, direction: str, speed: int = 50) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"连续对焦移动 - 通过 PTZ continuous 接口。\n\n        direction: 'near' 或 'far'\n        speed: 0-100\n        \"\"\"\n        # focus 速度范围 -10 到 10\n        focus_speed = round(speed / 10.0)  # speed=50 -> 5\n        if direction == 'near':\n            focus_speed = -focus_speed\n        return self.continuous_move(pan=0, tilt=0, zoom=0, focus=focus_speed)\n\n    def focus_move_absolute(self, direction: str, step: int = 50) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"绝对对焦移动 - 通过 focusConfiguration 的 focusPos。\n\n        direction: 'near' (减小 focusPos) 或 'far' (增大 focusPos)\n        step: 移动步长 (0-100)\n        注意: 由于无法读取当前 focusPos，此方法使用估算值\n        \"\"\"\n        # focusPos 范围约 0-1000\n        # 近似估算：每次调用增减固定步长\n        focus_step = step * 5  # step=50 -> 250\n        \n        # 先切换到手动模式\n        self.set_focus_mode('manual')\n        \n        # 使用 PTZ continuous 作为替代方案（设备不支持读取 focusPos）\n        return self.focus_move_continuous(direction, step)\n"}],"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/core/ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":117091,"output":891,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117982,"cost":{"input":0.117091,"output":0.0028512000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1199422}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781205604690,"responseId":"cht000db5da@dx19eb8209cc9b828232"}}
