{"type":"message","id":"67996d32","parentId":"ae6caf1b","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:21:38.253Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1aff7f5560c942838114c8bd","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Connect ===\r\n{\"success\":true,\"message\":\"设备已连接\"}\r\n=== Focus Far (3s) ===\r\n{\"success\":true,\"message\":\"PTZ focus-far (speed=60)\"}{\"success\":true,\"message\":\"停止成功\"}\r\n=== Focus Near (3s) ===\r\n{\"success\":true,\"message\":\"PTZ focus-near (speed=60)\"}{\"success\":true,\"message\":\"停止成功\"}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7544,"aggregated":"=== Connect ===\r\n{\"success\":true,\"message\":\"设备已连接\"}\r\n=== Focus Far (3s) ===\r\n{\"success\":true,\"message\":\"PTZ focus-far (speed=60)\"}{\"success\":true,\"message\":\"停止成功\"}\r\n=== Focus Near (3s) ===\r\n{\"success\":true,\"message\":\"PTZ focus-near (speed=60)\"}{\"success\":true,\"message\":\"停止成功\"}","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781205698253}}
{"type":"message","id":"8f8bfa24","parentId":"67996d32","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:21:46.858Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**API 调用成功！** \n\n让我验证 ISAPI 请求是否正确发送："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-e0a481495c0e4016a6f984ad36c0bc2f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 直接测试官方 Focus 端点 ===\" && curl -s -X PUT \"http://192.168.5.72/ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus\" --digest -u admin:Nftw1357 -H \"Content-Type: application/xml\" -d '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?><FocusData><focus>60</focus></FocusData>' --max-time 5 2>&1 && Start-Sleep -Seconds 3 && curl -s -X PUT \"http://192.168.5.72/ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus\" --digest -u admin:Nftw1357 -H \"Content-Type: application/xml\" -d '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?><FocusData><focus>0</focus></FocusData>' --max-time 5 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":113537,"output":227,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113764,"cost":{"input":0.113537,"output":0.0007264000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1142634}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781205698256,"responseId":"cht000d8c60@dx19eb8220879ba5b442"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6aa3a493","parentId":"8f8bfa24","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:21:50.352Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-e0a481495c0e4016a6f984ad36c0bc2f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== ֱ�Ӳ��Թٷ� Focus �˵� ===\r\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?><ResponseStatus version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n<requestURL></requestURL>\n<statusCode>1</statusCode>\n<statusString>OK</statusString>\n<subStatusCode>ok</subStatusCode>\n</ResponseStatus>\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?><ResponseStatus version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n<requestURL></requestURL>\n<statusCode>1</statusCode>\n<statusString>OK</statusString>\n<subStatusCode>ok</subStatusCode>\n</ResponseStatus>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3458,"aggregated":"=== ֱ�Ӳ��Թٷ� Focus �˵� ===\r\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?><ResponseStatus version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n<requestURL></requestURL>\n<statusCode>1</statusCode>\n<statusString>OK</statusString>\n<subStatusCode>ok</subStatusCode>\n</ResponseStatus>\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?><ResponseStatus version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n<requestURL></requestURL>\n<statusCode>1</statusCode>\n<statusString>OK</statusString>\n<subStatusCode>ok</subStatusCode>\n</ResponseStatus>","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781205710352}}
{"type":"message","id":"14dbfa0e","parentId":"6aa3a493","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:22:14.865Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**官方端点直接测试也成功！**\n\n## 修复完成\n\n**确认的方法**：\n\n| 项目 | 官方方法 |\n|------|----------|\n| Focus 移动 | `PUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus` |\n| 请求格式 | `<FocusData><focus>60</focus></FocusData>` |\n| focus 值 | 正数=后移（远焦），负数=前移（近焦），0=停止 |\n| 范围 | 约 -100 到 100 |\n| Focus 停止 | `<FocusData><focus>0</focus></FocusData>` |\n\n**对比之前的方法**：\n\n| 之前（错误） | 现在（正确） |\n|------|------|\n| `PUT /PTZCtrl/channels/1/continuous` | `PUT /System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus` |\n| `<ptzSpeed><focus>8</focus></ptzSpeed>` | `<FocusData><focus>60</focus></FocusData>` |\n| 设备 capabilities 不支持 | **官方界面使用的端点** |\n\n**AstroHub 修改**：\n- `focus_move_continuous()` - 改用官方 Focus 端点\n- `focus_stop()` - 发送 `<focus>0</focus>` 停止\n- `stop_move()` - 同时停止 PTZ 和 Focus"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":113738,"output":296,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114034,"cost":{"input":0.11373799999999999,"output":0.0009472,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.11468519999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781205710354,"responseId":"cht000d832e@dx19eb8223c1ab85e102"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d6cb9918","parentId":"14dbfa0e","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:23:41.261Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-06-12 03:16:58 GMT+8] Exec completed (tidal-em, code 0) :: === 1. ��������ͷ: http://192.168.5.72/ === === 2. ��ǰ URL: http://192.168.5.72/doc/index.html#/portal/login === ����: ��¼ === 3. ���� PTZ ������� === ����: http://192.168.5.72/ISA…\nSystem (untrusted): [2026-06-12 03:18:29 GMT+8] Exec completed (good-mea, code 0) :: ontentMgmt/channels/1/cloudStorage/1/capabilities?security=1&iv=66ea0679ada0825875105f9a78dab728 GET Smart/storageDetection/rwlock/capabilities GET Event/triggersCap GET ContentMg…\nSystem (untrusted): [2026-06-12 03:20:04 GMT+8] Exec completed (crisp-la, code 0) :: patterns [6.70s] PUT System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus POST DATA: <?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?><FocusData><focus>-60</focus></FocusData> [6.70s] PUT System/Video/input…\nSystem (untrusted): [2026-06-12 03:21:14 GMT+8] Exec completed (marine-f, code 1) :: ce_manager] DeviceManager ��ʼ�����, storage=C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\data\\config\\ptz_config.json INFO: Application startup complete. ERROR: [Errno 1004…\n\nAn async command you ran earlier has completed. The result is shown in the system messages above. Handle the result internally. Do not relay it to the user unless explicitly requested.\nCurrent time: Friday, June 12th, 2026 - 03:23 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-06-11 19:23 UTC"}],"timestamp":1781205821254}}
{"type":"message","id":"95f8afa4","parentId":"d6cb9918","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:24:07.200Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到。\n\n## v5.47 Focus 修复确认\n\n**通过 Playwright 捕获海康官方 Web 界面请求，确认了正确的 Focus 控制方法：**\n\n### 官方 Focus ISAPI 端点\n\n```\nPUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus\n```\n\n**请求格式**：\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<FocusData>\n  <focus>-60</focus>  <!-- 负数=前移(近焦)，正数=后移(远焦) -->\n</FocusData>\n```\n\n**停止请求**：\n```xml\n<FocusData>\n  <focus>0</focus>\n</FocusData>\n```\n\n### AstroHub 已修复\n\n| 函数 | 修改 |\n|------|------|\n| `focus_move_continuous()` | 改用官方 `/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus` 端点 |\n| `focus_stop()` | 发送 `<focus>0</focus>` |\n| `stop_move()` | 同时停止 PTZ 和 Focus |\n\n### 测试验证\n\n- ✅ Playwright 捕获到官方界面发送：`PUT System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus` with `<focus>-60</focus>`\n- ✅ AstroHub API 测试成功：`focus-far` / `focus-near` 返回 OK\n- ✅ 直接 ISAPI 测试成功\n\n**老板可以通过 AstroHub Web 界面点击 Focus 按钮测试效果。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":114578,"output":331,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114909,"cost":{"input":0.114578,"output":0.0010592000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1156372}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781205821262,"responseId":"cht000dd5d4@dx19eb8241122b828232"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1eb7e2c7","parentId":"95f8afa4","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:31:25.127Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"32935\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-06-12 03:31 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n当前的astrohub上，依然无法手动移动焦点。你的判断是有问题的，继续使用官方IP访问摄像头，再配置-图像标签，画面右侧有移动焦点的按钮，对应显示文字是聚焦- 聚焦+，继续找到正确方式"}],"timestamp":1781206285121}}
{"type":"message","id":"9e9d7336","parentId":"1eb7e2c7","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:31:59.240Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到。让我重新通过 Playwright 访问官方界面的配置-图像页面，找到正确的 Focus 控制方法。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d7a1faac7de646958d91ca13","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\n访问海康摄像头官方界面 - 配置-图像页面\n找到正确的 Focus 控制方法\n\"\"\"\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\nimport time\n\nIP = \"192.168.5.72\"\nUSERNAME = \"admin\"\nPASSWORD = \"Nftw1357\"\n\ndef test():\n    with open(\"focus_capture_log.txt\", \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as log_file:\n        def log(msg):\n            print(msg)\n            log_file.write(msg + \"\\n\")\n        \n        with sync_playwright() as p:\n            browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True)\n            context = browser.new_context(ignore_https_errors=True)\n            page = context.new_page()\n            \n            # 捕获所有请求\n            all_requests = []\n            def capture(req):\n                if 'ISAPI' in req.url:\n                    all_requests.append({\n                        'time': time.time(),\n                        'method': req.method,\n                        'url': req.url.split('/ISAPI/')[-1] if '/ISAPI/' in req.url else req.url,\n                        'data': req.post_data or ''\n                    })\n            page.on('request', capture)\n            \n            log(\"=== 1. 登录摄像头 ===\")\n            page.goto(f\"http://{IP}/doc/index.html\", timeout=30000)\n            page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n            \n            try:\n                page.fill('input[placeholder*=\"用户名\"], input[id*=\"username\"], input[name=\"username\"]', USERNAME, timeout=5000)\n                page.fill('input[type=\"password\"]', PASSWORD, timeout=5000)\n                page.click('button:has-text(\"登录\"), button[type=\"submit\"]', timeout=5000)\n                page.wait_for_timeout(5000)\n                log(\"   登录成功\")\n            except Exception as e:\n                log(f\"   登录: {e}\")\n            \n            log(\"\\n=== 2. 进入配置-图像页面 ===\")\n            # 海康新版界面路径\n            config_urls = [\n                f\"http://{IP}/doc/index.html#/config/image\",\n                f\"http://{IP}/doc/index.html#/configure/image\",\n                f\"http://{IP}/doc/index.html#/image\",\n            ]\n            \n            for url in config_urls:\n                try:\n                    log(f\"   尝试: {url}\")\n                    page.goto(url, timeout=10000)\n                    page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n                    if 'image' in page.url.lower() or 'config' in page.url.lower():\n                        log(f\"   成功: {page.url}\")\n                        break\n                except:\n                    pass\n            \n            log(f\"   当前 URL: {page.url}\")\n            \n            # 查找聚焦按钮\n            log(\"\\n=== 3. 查找聚焦按钮 ===\")\n            \n            # 等待页面加载\n            page.wait_for_timeout(5000)\n            \n            # 查找包含\"聚焦\"的元素\n            focus_selectors = [\n                'button:has-text(\"聚焦\")',\n                'button:has-text(\"聚焦+\")',\n                'button:has-text(\"聚焦-\")',\n                '[title*=\"聚焦\"]',\n                '[class*=\"focus\"]',\n                'span:has-text(\"聚焦\")',\n                '.focus-btn',\n                '.focus-button',\n            ]\n            \n            focus_elements = []\n            for sel in focus_selectors:\n                try:\n                    elems = page.locator(sel)\n                    count = elems.count()\n                    if count > 0:\n                        for i in range(count):\n                            try:\n                                elem = elems.nth(i)\n                                text = elem.text_content() or ''\n                                title = elem.get_attribute('title') or ''\n                                cls = elem.get_attribute('class') or ''\n                                onclick = elem.get_attribute('onclick') or ''\n                                focus_elements.append({\n                                    'selector': sel,\n                                    'text': text.strip(),\n                                    'title': title,\n                                    'class': cls[:80],\n                                    'onclick': onclick[:100]\n                                })\n                            except:\n                                pass\n                except:\n                    pass\n            \n            if focus_elements:\n                log(\"   找到聚焦相关元素:\")\n                for fe in focus_elements:\n                    log(f\"     {fe}\")\n            else:\n                log(\"   未找到聚焦按钮，尝试查找所有按钮...\")\n                all_btns = page.locator('button')\n                count = all_btns.count()\n                log(f\"   页面共有 {count} 个按钮\")\n                for i in range(min(count, 30)):\n                    try:\n                        btn = all_btns.nth(i)\n                        text = btn.text_content() or ''\n                        if '焦' in text or 'focus' in text.lower() or '+' in text or '-' in text:\n                            log(f\"     按钮 {i}: '{text.strip()}'\")\n                    except:\n                        pass\n            \n            # 清空请求记录，准备捕获聚焦操作\n            all_requests.clear()\n            t0 = time.time()\n            \n            # 尝试点击聚焦按钮\n            log(\"\\n=== 4. 点击聚焦+ 按钮 ===\")\n            \n            # 查找并点击\"聚焦+\"或类似按钮\n            clicked = False\n            click_selectors = [\n                'button:has-text(\"聚焦+\")',\n                'button:has-text(\"聚焦 +\")',\n                'button >> :text(\"聚焦+\")',\n                'button >> :text(\"聚焦 +\")',\n            ]\n            \n            for sel in click_selectors:\n                try:\n                    btn = page.locator(sel).first\n                    if btn.count() > 0:\n                        log(f\"   找到按钮: {sel}\")\n                        btn.click()\n                        clicked = True\n                        page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n                        break\n                except:\n                    pass\n            \n            if not clicked:\n                # 尝试通过文本查找\n                log(\"   尝试通过文本查找...\")\n                try:\n                    btns = page.locator('button')\n                    for i in range(btns.count()):\n                        btn = btns.nth(i)\n                        text = btn.text_content() or ''\n                        if '聚焦' in text and ('+' in text or '-' in text):\n                            log(f\"   找到按钮: '{text}'\")\n                            btn.click()\n                            page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n                            clicked = True\n                            break\n                except:\n                    pass\n            \n            # 打印捕获的请求\n            log(f\"\\n=== 5. 捕获的 ISAPI 请求 (点击后 {len(all_requests)} 条) ===\")\n            for r in all_requests:\n                elapsed = r['time'] - t0\n                log(f\"   [{elapsed:.2f}s] {r['method']} {r['url']}\")\n                if r['data']:\n                    log(f\"      POST: {r['data'][:300]}\")\n            \n            # 截图\n            page.screenshot(path=\"hikvision_config_image.png\", full_page=True)\n            log(\"\\n截图已保存: hikvision_config_image.png\")\n            \n            # 保存页面 HTML\n            html = page.content()\n            with open(\"hikvision_config_image.html\", \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n                f.write(html)\n            log(\"页面 HTML 已保存: hikvision_config_image.html\")\n            \n            browser.close()\n            \n            return all_requests\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    test()","path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/tests/hikvision_config_