{"type":"message","id":"25be1810","parentId":"260bb4d0","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:36:29.496Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**确认了！官方界面使用的 Focus ISAPI：**\n\n```\nPUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus\n```\n\n**请求格式**：\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<FocusData>\n  <focus>60</focus>   <!-- 聚焦+ (后移/远焦) -->\n</FocusData>\n\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<FocusData>\n  <focus>-60</focus>  <!-- 聚焦- (前移/近焦) -->\n</FocusData>\n\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<FocusData>\n  <focus>0</focus>    <!-- 停止 -->\n</FocusData>\n```\n\n**这与我之前的修改一致！** \n\n让我检查 AstroHub 的代码是否正确使用这个端点："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_46470677d58e4d2fa6e96e05","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 测试 AstroHub Focus API ===\" && curl -s -X POST \"http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/move\" -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"direction\":\"focus-far\",\"speed\":60}' && Start-Sleep -Seconds 3 && curl -s -X POST \"http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/stop\" && echo \"\" && echo \"=== 检查服务日志 ===\" && Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\focus_capture.txt\" -Tail 20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":135804,"output":349,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136153,"cost":{"input":0.13580399999999998,"output":0.0011168,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.13692079999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781206577460,"responseId":"cht000dfa55@dx19eb82f73c5ba5a412"}}
