{"type":"message","id":"6b594dc1","parentId":"3052e647","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:36:47.779Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**ISAPI 端点正确！** 返回 OK。\n\n## 最终确认\n\n**官方 Focus ISAPI 端点**：\n- **端点**: `PUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus`\n- **请求**: `<FocusData><focus>60</focus></FocusData>`\n- **参数**: 正数=后移(远焦)，负数=前移(近焦)，0=停止\n- **范围**: 约 ±100\n\n**AstroHub 已正确使用此端点！** 代码修改已完成。\n\n**老板需要通过 AstroHub Web 界面测试**：\n1. 打开 AstroHub Console 页面\n2. 点击并按住 \"前移\" 按钮 2-3 秒\n3. 点击并按住 \"后移\" 按钮 2-3 秒\n4. 观察画面清晰度变化\n\n如果画面清晰度有变化，说明功能正常。如果没有变化，可能是设备问题或需要在手动对焦模式下操作。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":137104,"output":214,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137318,"cost":{"input":0.137104,"output":0.0006848000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.13778880000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781206598569,"responseId":"cht000d0d21@dx19eb82fc58cb8ab282"}}
