{"type":"message","id":"4666c083","parentId":"6478f925","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:37:54.040Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到。\n\n## 最终确认\n\n**通过 Playwright 捕获海康官方 Web 界面，确认了正确的 Focus 控制方法：**\n\n### 官方 ISAPI 端点\n```\nPUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus\n```\n\n### 请求格式\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<FocusData>\n  <focus>60</focus>   <!-- 正数=后移/远焦 -->\n</FocusData>\n\n<FocusData>\n  <focus>-60</focus>  <!-- 负数=前移/近焦 -->\n</FocusData>\n\n<FocusData>\n  <focus>0</focus>    <!-- 停止 -->\n</FocusData>\n```\n\n### AstroHub 已正确使用此端点\n\n| 功能 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| Focus API | ✅ 使用正确的 ISAPI 端点 |\n| focus-far | ✅ 发送 `<focus>60</focus>` |\n| focus-near | ✅ 发送 `<focus>-60</focus>` |\n| stop | ✅ 发送 `<focus>0</focus>` |\n\n**老板请通过 AstroHub Web 界面测试 Focus 功能，观察画面清晰度变化。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":137329,"output":273,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137602,"cost":{"input":0.137329,"output":0.0008736000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1382026}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781206632587,"responseId":"cht000d443a@dx19eb830b696ba5d322"}}
