{"type":"message","id":"241c7c5f","parentId":"652ce668","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:47:11.791Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"100 和 60 都返回 OK。但官方界面使用的是 60。\n\n**修正**：官方界面使用 `focus=±60`，不是 `±100`。\n\n让我修改 AstroHub 代码，使用官方的速度值 60："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5c18edba009040509330c7da","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1120,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/core/ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":138459,"output":95,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138554,"cost":{"input":0.138459,"output":0.000304,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.138763}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781207222860,"responseId":"cht000d8270@dx19eb8394cc1ba5e412"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a024892","parentId":"241c7c5f","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:47:11.798Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5c18edba009040509330c7da","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        mode: 'auto', 'manual', 'semiautomatic'\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        mode_upper = mode.upper()\r\n        endpoint = f\"/Image/channels/{self.channel}/focusConfiguration\"\r\n        xml = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<FocusConfiguration version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n  <focusStyle>{mode_upper}</focusStyle>\r\n  <focusLimited>300</focusLimited>\r\n</FocusConfiguration>'''\r\n        result = self.client.put(endpoint, xml)\r\n        return result.status_code == 200\r\n\r\n    def focus_move_continuous(self, direction: str, speed: int = 50) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"连续对焦移动 - 通过官方 Focus 端点。\r\n\r\n        direction: 'near' (前移/近焦) 或 'far' (后移/远焦)\r\n        speed: 0-100\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        endpoint = f\"/System/Video/inputs/channels/{self.channel}/focus\"\r\n        \r\n        # focus 速度范围约 -100 到 100\r\n        # near (前移) 负值，far (后移) 正值\r\n        focus_speed = speed\r\n        if direction == 'near':\r\n            focus_speed = -speed\r\n        \r\n        xml = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<FocusData>\r\n  <focus>{focus_speed}</focus>\r\n</FocusData>'''\r\n\n[1576 more lines in file. Use offset=1150 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781207231798}}
{"type":"message","id":"1ac3792a","parentId":"0a024892","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:47:28.787Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"当前代码直接使用 `speed` 值。官方使用固定值 60。\n\n让我修改为使用官方的方式：用户输入 speed 0-100，映射到实际 focus 速度（官方用 60）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_371cb289c9f248dfb5f73dc7","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def focus_move_continuous(self, direction: str, speed: int = 50) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"连续对焦移动 - 通过官方 Focus 端点。\n\n        direction: 'near' (前移/近焦) 或 'far' (后移/远焦)\n        speed: 0-100，映射到官方 focus 速度\n        \n        官方界面使用 focus=60 作为默认速度。\n        \"\"\"\n        endpoint = f\"/System/Video/inputs/channels/{self.channel}/focus\"\n        \n        # 官方界面使用固定值 60\n        # speed 0-100 映射到 0-60\n        focus_speed = int(speed * 60 / 100)  # speed=50 -> 30, speed=100 -> 60\n        \n        if direction == 'near':\n            focus_speed = -focus_speed\n        \n        xml = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<FocusData>\n  <focus>{focus_speed}</focus>\n</FocusData>'''","oldText":"    def focus_move_continuous(self, direction: str, speed: int = 50) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"连续对焦移动 - 通过官方 Focus 端点。\n\n        direction: 'near' (前移/近焦) 或 'far' (后移/远焦)\n        speed: 0-100\n        \"\"\"\n        endpoint = f\"/System/Video/inputs/channels/{self.channel}/focus\"\n        \n        # focus 速度范围约 -100 到 100\n        # near (前移) 负值，far (后移) 正值\n        focus_speed = speed\n        if direction == 'near':\n            focus_speed = -speed\n        \n        xml = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<FocusData>\n  <focus>{focus_speed}</focus>\n</FocusData>'''"}],"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/core/ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":138967,"output":547,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":139514,"cost":{"input":0.138967,"output":0.0017504,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.140717400000