{"type":"message","id":"1fa5000b","parentId":"9dbc31f8","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:59:12.109Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"前端代码：\n```javascript\nvar speed = parseInt(document.getElementById('ptzSpeed').value);\n```\n\n`ptzSpeed` 是一个滑块，默认值是多少？让我查看 HTML："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-b9677b20bfb74a5d9f8bc900ee48790e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Select-String -Path \"src/web/includes/console.html\" -Pattern \"ptzSpeed\" -Context 0,3"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":136288,"output":91,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136379,"cost":{"input":0.136288,"output":0.00029120000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.13657919999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781207944808,"responseId":"cht000dd5a1@dx19eb8445153ba5a412"}}
