{"type":"message","id":"c18862f9","parentId":"0d8af0f4","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:59:31.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**找到了！**\n\n滑块默认值是 `value=\"50\"`，范围 `min=\"1\" max=\"100\"`。\n\n所以：\n- 用户点击按钮时，speed 默认是 **50**\n- 用户可以通过滑块调整 1-100\n\n**映射逻辑**：\n- `speed=50` → `focus=30`（官方用 60）\n- `speed=100` → `focus=60`\n\n**问题**：官方界面使用固定值 60，而 AstroHub 用户默认 speed=50 只会发送 focus=30。\n\n**修复**：直接使用官方的固定值 60，不需要映射："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5422a605f21340419125fd51","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def focus_move_continuous(self, direction: str, speed: int = 50) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"连续对焦移动 - 通过官方 Focus 端点。\n\n        direction: 'near' (前移/近焦) 或 'far' (后移/远焦)\n        speed: 用户输入 1-100，但官方界面使用固定值 60\n        \n        官方界面: 点击聚焦按钮时发送 focus=±60\n        \"\"\"\n        endpoint = f\"/System/Video/inputs/channels/{self.channel}/focus\"\n        \n        # 官方界面使用固定值 60，忽略用户 speed 输入\n        focus_speed = 60\n        \n        if direction == 'near':\n            focus_speed = -focus_speed\n        \n        xml = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<FocusData>\n  <focus>{focus_speed}</focus>\n</FocusData>'''","oldText":"    def focus_move_continuous(self, direction: str, speed: int = 50) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"连续对焦移动 - 通过官方 Focus 端点。\n\n        direction: 'near' (前移/近焦) 或 'far' (后移/远焦)\n        speed: 0-100，映射到官方 focus 速度\n        \n        官方界面使用 focus=60 作为默认速度。\n        \"\"\"\n        endpoint = f\"/System/Video/inputs/channels/{self.channel}/focus\"\n        \n        # 官方界面使用固定值 60\n        # speed 0-100 映射到 0-60\n        focus_speed = int(speed * 60 / 100)  # speed=50 -> 30, speed=100 -> 60\n        \n        if direction == 'near':\n            focus_speed = -focus_speed\n        \n        xml = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<FocusData>\n  <focus>{focus_speed}</focus>\n</FocusData>'''"}],"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/core/ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":143742,"output":653,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144395,"cost":{"input":0.14374199999999998,"output":0.0020896,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.14583159999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781207952618,"responseId":"cht000df72d@dx19eb8446f72ba5c342"}}
