{"type":"message","id":"6cc5e26f","parentId":"39796c50","timestamp":"2026-06-11T20:00:25.365Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 修复完成\n\n**最终方案**：\n- 用户点击 Focus 按钮，前端发送 `speed=50`（默认值）\n- 后端**忽略 speed 参数**，直接使用官方固定值 `focus=±60`\n\n**这与官方界面行为一致**：无论用户调整什么滑块，Focus 操作都使用固定速度 60。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":138013,"output":71,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138084,"cost":{"input":0.138013,"output":0.00022720000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1382402}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781208018480,"responseId":"cht000df632@dx19eb845733cb9ca102"}}
