{"type":"message","id":"b15a69af","parentId":"50a5afff","timestamp":"2026-06-11T20:19:55.718Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 验证结果\n\n**AstroHub Focus 功能验证通过** ✅\n\n| 验证项 | 结果 |\n|--------|------|\n| 前端发送 | `speed=60` ✅ |\n| 后端 ISAPI | `PUT /System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus` ✅ |\n| ISAPI 直接测试 | HTTP 200 OK ✅ |\n| Focus 停止 | 发送 `<focus>0</focus>` ✅ |"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":144275,"output":103,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144378,"cost":{"input":0.144275,"output":0.00032960000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1446046}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781209185455,"responseId":"cht000d9d05@dx19eb8573f76b894142"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8998eb0a","parentId":"b15a69af","timestamp":"2026-06-11T20:23:37.772Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-06-12 04:19:12 GMT+8] Exec completed (gentle-v, code 0) :: 4. ��� Focus Near (ǰ��) ��ť === �ѵ������ס 3 �� === 5. ����� PTZ/Focus ���� === [0.06s] POST move DATA: {\"direction\":\"focus-far\",\"speed\":60} [5.12s] POST move DATA: {\"direction\":\"f…\n\nAn async command you ran earlier has completed. The result is shown in the system messages above. Handle the result internally. Do not relay it to the user unless explicitly requested.\nCurrent time: Friday, June 12th, 2026 - 04:23 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-06-11 20:23 UTC"}],"timestamp":1781209417766}}
{"type":"message","id":"7b34c7d4","parentId":"8998eb0a","timestamp":"2026-06-11T20:23:47.101Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到。\n\n## v5.47 Focus 验证完成 ✅\n\n**验证结果**：\n- 前端发送 `speed=60`\n- 后端发送 `PUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus`\n- ISAPI 返回 HTTP 200 OK\n- Focus 停止发送 `<focus>0</focus>`\n\n**功能已生效，老板请通过 AstroHub Web 界面测试实际效果。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":152160,"output":97,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":152257,"cost":{"input":0.15216,"output":0.0003104,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.15247039999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781209417772,"responseId":"cht000dc39d@dx19eb85aca69b9ca102"}}
