{"type":"message","id":"9d9f85f7","parentId":"e11c8eab","timestamp":"2026-06-11T20:37:36.080Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1781210224053,"errorMessage":"Request timed out."}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f939fcd","parentId":"9d9f85f7","timestamp":"2026-06-11T20:38:02.342Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到。复盘并更新记忆。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_22d6b789bb7e4e60a5bc3390","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# MEMORY.md\n\n## 海康 ISAPI 关键发现\n\n### Focus 控制端点（重要）\n- **正确端点**: `PUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus`\n- **请求格式**:\n  ```xml\n  <?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n  <FocusData>\n    <focus>60</focus>   <!-- 正数=后移/远焦，负数=前移/近焦 -->\n  </FocusData>\n  ```\n- **停止**: `<focus>0</focus>`\n- **固定值**: 官方界面使用固定值 60，不是可调参数\n\n### PTZ 控制端点\n- **Continuous**: `PUT /ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/continuous`\n- **速度范围**: pan/tilt/zoom 都是 -10 到 10（ISAPI 2.0 规范）\n- **注意**: 设备 capabilities 可能不显示 ContinuousFocusSpace，但 Focus 需用单独端点\n\n### OSD 控制端点\n- **PTZ OSD**: `PUT /ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/PTZOSDDisplay` (~300ms)\n- **OSD Info**: `PUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/overlays` (~2-4秒，设备固有延迟)\n- **ns0: 命名空间**: `ET.tostring` 会产生 `ns0:` 前缀，海康拒绝，需字符串替换移除\n\n## 海康摄像头型号\n- **型号**: iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A\n- **Zoom 范围**: 10-320\n- **Pan/Tilt 范围**: 0-3600 / -200-900\n- **认证**: Digest Auth\n\n## Playwright 捕获官方请求方法\n1. 登录后进入预览页面\n2. 聚焦按钮在预览页面右侧，title=\"聚焦 +\" / title=\"聚焦 -\"\n3. 使用 `page.on('request', ...)` 捕获 ISAPI 请求\n4. 官方界面是动态加载的 Vue 应用，需等待足够时间\n\n## 常见错误\n\n### 速度缩放问题\n- **错误**: 在 `ptz_move` 和 `continuous_move` 两层都做缩放\n- **修复**: 只在 `continuous_move` 做一次缩放，或直接传原始值\n\n### Focus 端点错误\n- **错误**: 使用 PTZ continuous 的 `<focus>` 参数（设备不支持）\n- **修复**: 使用单独的 `/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus` 端点\n\n### 前端按钮事件\n- **错误**: 只用 `onmousedown` 没有处理 `mouseup`\n- **修复**: 添加 `onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\"` 或使用全局 mouseup 监听\n\n## 项目配置\n- **AstroHub 端口**: 10280\n- **设备 IP**: 192.168.5.72\n- **认证**: admin / Nftw1357\n","path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":152517,"output":723,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":153240,"cost":{"input":0.15251699999999999,"output":0.0023136000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.15483059999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781210258481,"responseId":"cht000d70c3@dx19eb8679f1cba60352"}}
