{"type":"message","id":"971d1ab9","parentId":"2909f873","timestamp":"2026-06-11T20:38:21.959Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"更新自我改进文件："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_66b1a1aba0d34fd1a35e0fa8","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# v5.47 Focus 修复复盘\n\n## 问题描述\n用户反馈 AstroHub 无法手动移动焦点，点击前移/后移按钮无效。\n\n## 问题根因\n1. **使用了错误的 ISAPI 端点**\n   - 错误：`PUT /PTZCtrl/channels/1/continuous` 中的 `<focus>` 参数\n   - 正确：`PUT /System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus` 单独端点\n\n2. **设备 capabilities 不显示 ContinuousFocusSpace**\n   - 但 ISAPI 接口仍接受请求（返回 OK）\n   - 实际上设备不执行 PTZ continuous 中的 focus 指令\n\n## 解决方案\n通过 Playwright 打开海康官方 Web 界面，捕获实际使用的 ISAPI 请求：\n- 进入预览页面\n- 点击\"聚焦+\"按钮\n- 捕获到 `PUT /System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus` 请求\n- XML 格式：`<FocusData><focus>60</focus></FocusData>`\n\n## 关键发现\n1. **官方使用固定值 60**\n   - 不是可调参数，直接固定使用 60\n   - 正数=后移，负数=前移，0=停止\n\n2. **Focus 控制独立于 PTZ**\n   - Focus 有单独的 ISAPI 端点\n   - 不通过 PTZ continuous 接口\n\n## 修复步骤\n1. 修改 `focus_move_continuous()` 使用 `/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus`\n2. 前端 `ptzFocus()` 直接传固定值 `speed=60`\n3. 后端忽略用户输入的 speed，始终使用 60\n\n## 验证方法\n```bash\n# 直接测试 ISAPI\ncurl -X PUT \"http://192.168.5.72/ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus\" \\\n  --digest -u admin:Nftw1357 \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/xml\" \\\n  -d '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?><FocusData><focus>60</focus></FocusData>'\n```\n\n## 教训\n- **不要推测**，必须通过官方界面捕获实际请求\n- 设备 capabilities 可能不完整，实际功能需要验证\n- 使用 Playwright 捕获官方请求是可靠方法\n","path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/.learnings/v547_focus_fix.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":145946,"output":563,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146509,"cost":{"input":0.145946,"output":0.0018016000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.14774759999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781210282367,"responseId":"cht000d44d7@dx19eb86826e4b9ca102"}}
