{"type":"message","id":"d8929fd9","parentId":"4135c2f8","timestamp":"2026-06-11T20:38:37.209Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"更新 HEARTBEAT："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_127ba03191244cb78a12d12e","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 心跳与任务状态\n\n**最后更新**: 2026-06-12 04:36\n**状态**: v5.47 Focus 修复完成\n**工作空间**: C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\n### v5.47 修复内容\n| # | 问题 | 状态 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | Zoom 速度缩放 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 2 | Focus 端点错误 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 3 | Focus 固定值 60 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 4 | OSD ns0: 前缀 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 5 | OSD Info 延迟 | ⚠️ 设备特性 |\n\n### 关键发现\n- **Focus ISAPI**: `PUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus`\n- **Focus 格式**: `<FocusData><focus>±60</focus></FocusData>`\n- **固定值**: 官方使用固定值 60，不是可调参数\n\n### 验证命令\n```bash\n# Focus 测试\ncurl -X PUT \"http://192.168.5.72/ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus\" \\\n  --digest -u admin:Nftw1357 \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/xml\" \\\n  -d '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?><FocusData><focus>60</focus></FocusData>'\n\n# AstroHub API\ncurl -X POST \"http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/move\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"direction\":\"focus-far\",\"speed\":60}'\n```\n\n### 正确端口\n- **AstroHub**: 10280\n- **摄像头 ISAPI**: 80\n- **摄像头 WebSocket**: 7681\n","path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":153892,"output":465,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":154357,"cost":{"input":0.153892,"output":0.0014880000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.15538}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781210301986,"responseId":"cht000d5304@dx19eb8684cdfba5e412"}}
